SUNINDEX F:\DATA\ACCOUNTS.TXT,F:\DATA\ACCOUNTS.ISI;1-4
SUNINDEX F:\DATA\ACCOUNTS.TXT,F:\DATA\ACCTS430.ISI;6-35,1-4
